    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029331_32_6101-6175",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "6101-6175",
      "markText": "如果没有常景这篇墓志，慈庆八十六年的人生早如轻烟一般散入虚空，随她长灭的还有许多具有历史节点意义的事件与事实。幸亏有墓志，我们得以一窥那遥远的往昔。",
      "totalCount": 1620,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029331&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=6101&rangeEnd=6175",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55b32840813ab71f5g011671?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=6101&rangeEnd=6175"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029331_32_601-685",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "601-685",
      "markText": "后人读史到此，不禁悬心，但当时无人可见后人之所见，底层社会与遥远边地的强烈震荡，经僵化官僚体制的一层层过滤，传到洛阳朝廷时已大大衰减，至多如月光之下天渊池上的涟漪微澜。",
      "totalCount": 1212,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029331&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=601&rangeEnd=685",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55b32840813ab71f5g011671?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=601&rangeEnd=685"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029331_58_4149-4207",
      "chapterUid": 58,
      "range": "4149-4207",
      "markText": "历史和故事不同：故事有主人公，有开始，有结束，历史没有。故事是江河，有源头有终端。历史是海洋，没有起点，也没有终点。",
      "totalCount": 1188,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029331&chapterUid=58&rangeStart=4149&rangeEnd=4207",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55b32840813ab71f5g011671?chapterUid=58&rangeStart=4149&rangeEnd=4207"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029331_51_12292-12358",
      "chapterUid": 51,
      "range": "12292-12358",
      "markText": "据《魏书·彭城王传》，元勰被逼饮毒酒而死，在十八日深夜，十九日清晨“以褥裹尸，舆从屏门而出，载尸归第”，对元勰家人说他是喝酒喝死的。",
      "totalCount": 1092,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029331&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=12292&rangeEnd=12358",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55b32840813ab71f5g011671?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=12292&rangeEnd=12358"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029331_57_10577-10618",
      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "10577-10618",
      "markText": "一个团缩龙钟、昏眊重膇的老尼，在车水马龙、人山人海之中，不过是一片若有若无的轻尘。",
      "totalCount": 1088,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029331&chapterUid=57&rangeStart=10577&rangeEnd=10618",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55b32840813ab71f5g011671?chapterUid=57&rangeStart=10577&rangeEnd=10618"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029331_33_2213-2287",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "2213-2287",
      "markText": "这些看似虚美无实、空洞艳俗的谀辞，其实饱含着时代内容，后人可借以观察那时的规范和理想，而在一个礼法纠缠的社会，规范和理想又意味着荣辱明暗的巨大黑洞。",
      "totalCount": 1078,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029331&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=2213&rangeEnd=2287",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55b32840813ab71f5g011671?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=2213&rangeEnd=2287"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029331_33_4818-4909",
